articles.title: ‘Umpires didn’t know what was going on': Australia fume at Stoinis dismissal - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Marnus Labuschagne said Australia would seek clarity from the ICC and umpires about the debatable decisions of Steve Smith and Marcus Stoinis vs South Africa. | Cricket
